item.title: The Corruption of the DNC
item.description: Hillary Clinton, Martin O'Malley, and Bernie Sanders…three people who will never be president Disclaimer: I am NOT a Democrat. I am not endorsing any Democrats at all. I am not supporting Hillary Clinton, Bernie Sanders, and Martin O'Malley and I hope the Democratic nominee gets destroyed in the general election. None of them are capable of fixing this country. Now that the disclaimer is out of the way… Bernie Sanders is getting screwed.
